data.description: Views, views, and more views! Welcome home to this stunning home in the desirable Canyon View sub division. Greeted with cathedral ceilings, hardwood flooring and lots of natural lighting, you are sure to feel at home the moment you step inside. The large open kitchen with granite countertops, high cabinets and island is calling out the chef in you to create many delicious meals as you enjoy the coziness of a warm fire from the adjacent living room. Main and upper level has 3 bedrooms, 3 baths, and office. The lower level features a full and separate access living space, boosting an oversized bedroom with room for seating, kitchen, dining and living room perfect for multi-family/generational living. The beautifully landscaped yard is easily maintained with underground sprinkler system. No HOA and conveniently located, this home is price to sell!
